  <name>FreeFileSync</name>
  <summary>Visual folder comparison and synchronization</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      FreeFileSync is a folder comparison and synchronization software that
      creates and manages backup copies of your important files. Instead of
      copying every file every time, FreeFileSync determines the differences
      between a source and a target folder and transfers only the minimum
      amount of data needed.
    </p>
  </description>
